                Technical requirements for which the system was built: <br />
                <ul>
                    <li>.Net Core 5</li>
                    <li>Identity</li>
                    <li>Entity framework</li>
                    <li>FluentValidation for models and date booking rules (Web and API)</li>
                    <li>JQuery/Javascript for datepicker validation</li>
                    <li>Design Patterns (Repository)</li>
                    <li>SQL Server</li>
                </ul>
            </p>
        </details>
